[A] Cumulative Number of Reported Cases of Severe Acute Respiratory
Syndrome (SARS)
<http://www.who.int/csr/sarscountry/2003_03_29/en/>

From: 1 Nov 2002(1) To: 29 Mar 2003, 15:00 GMT+1

